---
title: Honey Miso Broccoli Donburi with Sweet Potato, Fried Eggs, Scallion Rice & Sriracha Mayo
description: Grain bowl–lovers, rejoice! This week, we’re serving up donburi, a Japanese rice bowl dish that can be endlessly customized with different proteins, veggies, and sauces. For this version, steamy scallion rice is layered with broccoli that’s tossed in a sweet and savory honey miso dressing, plus fried eggs and tender sweet potatoes. It’s all finished with a drizzle of Sriracha mayo and a sprinkle of scallion greens. Prepare to be totally bowled over!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/61670da9b2686e6428269b07-ed272fec.jpg
